{"tid":53651,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚發夢見到女神","createTime":"2016-12-24T22:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T02:33:14.000Z","uid":22342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c587ef6e4dcd0da82394388428514a2d35aa2a15","tid":53651,"uid":22342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T22:45:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的，琴日好早就訓<br />\n夢見同女神一齊行，一路同佢傾計，佢突然間同我講:邊個宜家拖住我就係我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依個時候，機會黎啦，飛雲！我一下捉住佢隻纖纖玉手，但係同一時間，唔知邊度有個撚屌出嚟拖住佢，佢話：唔好意思啊，佢快過你<br />\n我成個人崩潰左，點解！！！！！點解聖誕節發夢都溝唔到女神！！！！！點解我咁假嘅願望都實現唔到！！！！！點解我發夢都要俾人搶左女神！！！！！<br />\n佢講完之後，我仲要笑笑口話:咁好啦,我有嘢做，走先<br />\n點解個天要咁玩我！！！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c299a10738022269aed052f99b3e75a32f5ff335","tid":53651,"uid":22342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T22:46:38.000Z","msg":"屌！！！標題打撚錯！！！！！！"},{"pid":"e1d18155a62783827520006cb371e60b04d19a9f","tid":53651,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited